==========================
 Mirror for open source mirror site to sync files
==========================

Homepage: http://mirror.bjtu.edu.cn

Authors:
    Shang Yuanchun
    Bob Gao

For contributors and past developers see: 
    AUTHORS

==========================
Installation Instructions:
==========================

Build and install by running:

    $ python setup.py build
    $ sudo python setup.py install

    Or to a custom directory:

    $ sudo python setup.py install --root=/tmp

==========================
Contact/Support:
==========================

   Email: idealities@gmail.com

==========================
Features
==========================

 * 便捷的方式增加镜像
 * 不同镜像可设置优先级(1-10，10为最高)
 * 根据服务器负载和当前HTTP连接数来决定是否调度执行
 * 可配置多个上游，根据上游的状态自动切换
 * 失败时邮件通知
 * 磁盘状况报警
 * 可设置同步的超时时间
 * 支持两阶段同步(for ubuntu, debian等)
